P(\text{yellow first})=\frac15.\tag{i}
P(\text{yellow second})=\frac45\cdot\frac14=\frac15.\tag{ii}
P(\text{yellow third})=\frac{6}{10}\cdot\frac13=\frac15.\tag{iii}
P(\text{yellow fourth})=\frac{4}{10}\cdot\frac12=\frac15.\tag{iv}
\begin{align}P(\text{yellow chosen}) &= P(\text{yellow first})+P(\text{yellow second})+P(\text{yellow third})+P(\text{yellow fourth})\\ &= \frac15+\frac15+\frac15+\frac15\\ &= \frac45.\end{align}
\frac{\binom44}{\binom54}=\frac15
1-\frac15=\frac45
